San Antonio police-turned-cook and activist Joan Cheever has spent the past decade feeding the homeless from the back of her charity food truck , until earlier this month she was slapped with a $ 2,000 fine for her charitable efforts .
Cheever founded The Chow Train non-profit organization in 2005 , preparing hot meals in her personal pickup truck .
Mrs Cheever was issued a citation and a fine fine for failure to serve food out of a licensed food truck .